TextEquiv.Unicode: Andem illa tandem nobilis capta eſt
lla, illa Solyma cecidit, & caſus ſuos
Miata, credit vix ſibi; credit tamen
Vulcanus audax, dum vaga ſerpit lue,
Luditque in auro flammeis ſparſus globis.
Et dira tabo perlita, & ſparſæ incubans
Ga2æ paren tum gemuit inuiſum diem,
Graſſans cruentis in ſuos Reges dolis,
Tenetur inquam, noſtra tuto iam in Ioco
Ver ſantur odia: Iupiter cœlo imperet,
Riualis expers ſolus hic tertas regam.
Confecta demim bella ſunt cœlo auſpice.
A pollo, & ore niteat aurato fluens,
Dum læta pennis igneis vict oria
Nect it corollas, fama dum pernix citis
